      • validateScripts

        public Map<File,​String> validateScripts()
        Performs validation on the scripts in this whitelist. After invoking this method, validation will be performed on each script present in the whitelist. The result of the validation is a validation message which contains a human-readable description of the validation outcome or null if no problem was detected.
        Returns:
        a map with a script as key and a validation message as value
